威尔·史密斯谈好莱坞演员罢工：“这是我们职业的关键时刻” https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-hollywood-actors-strike-pivotal-moment-for-our-profession-3476622?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=will-smith-hollywood-actors-我们职业的关键时刻Adam StarkeyTue, 01 Aug 2023 20:56:59 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3476622 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威尔史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位演员在支持罢工的声明中反思了自己的职业生涯</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/will-smith-hollywood-actors-strike-pivotal-moment-for-our-profession-3476622">威尔·史密斯 (Will Smith) 评论好莱坞演员罢工的帖子：“这是我们职业的关键时刻”，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="威尔史密斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Will-Smith-new-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/will-smith">威尔·史密斯</a>将好莱坞演员和编剧的罢工描述为该行业的“关键时刻”。</p><p>史密斯在周五（7 月 28 日）的 Instagram 帖子中表达了他对美国编剧工会 (WGA) 和美国演员工会 (SAG-AFTRA) 罢工的支持。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/how-long-will-the-hollywood-actors-strike-last-3473291">好莱坞演员的罢工会持续多久？</a></strong></li></ul><p> “我想谈谈表演，”史密斯写道。 “正如你们中的一些人可能听说的那样，我的公会 @SAGAFTRA 正在与 WGA 的作家同事一起罢工。对于我们的职业来说，这是一个关键时刻。”</p><p>在与电影电视制片人联盟 (AMPTP) 的谈判破裂后，好莱坞演员工会于 7 月 13 日加入 WGA 罢工。两个工会都在寻求更好的薪酬、流转剩余资金以及防止人工智能技术使用的保障措施。</p><p>回顾自己的职业生涯，史密斯还表达了对导师亚伦·斯派瑟的感谢。 “我的演员生涯已经过去了 33 年，但仍有一些日子我感觉自己就像是那个来自费城的孩子，时间是借来的，尽管我知道自己一直以来都非常幸运地从事演员工作。这次。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/CvQWoYbSVAt/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none